body.description: "Introducing the Eagle Creek Pack-It Clean/Dirty Packing Cubes, the ultimate solution for efficient and organized travel. Designed to keep your clean and dirty clothes separated, these dual compartment travel organizers are a must-have for any trip. Say goodbye to mixing up your fresh garments with used ones! With these versatile travel cubes, you can easily pack and access your travel essentials. The dual compartments allow you to keep clean clothes neatly folded in one section, while the other section is perfect for storing dirty or wet items. This innovative design not only keeps your luggage organized but also ensures cleanliness and hygiene during your journey. Crafted with durability in mind, these packing cubes are made from high-quality materials that can withstand the rigors of travel. The lightweight construction helps to minimize the weight of your luggage while providing ample space for your belongings. You can trust these packing cubes to keep your items secure and protected throughout your trip. The Eagle Creek Pack-It Clean/Dirty Packing Cubes offer an easy and stress-free packing experience. Simply pack your items into the designated compartments, zip up the cubes, and place them in your luggage. When it's time to unpack, you'll be able to access your clean clothes separately from the dirty ones, saving you time and effort. Dimensions: 10 x 13.5 x 4 in."

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great item for those one or two night stands
reviews.reviewText: Bought this in a moment of weakness. Wasn't sure how it would work out. But on our first trip, we learned to like it! Great for those trips when you've flying. We used it to pack our underwear. We often fly into a city, spend a day or two in the city, then board the ship. With this, we could do the two day stay. And use the bag to store the dirty in the second section of the bag, and keep the clean pristine! Once we get to the ship, we dump the contents of the dirty side in their laundry bag and send it off.

reviews.reviewTitle: パッキングが楽になります
reviews.reviewText: 出張のパッキングの時に、今までは１００均のトラベルポーチを使っていましたが強度的にも、不安があり本品を購入しました。一部のレビューで本品に入れてから空気を抜くとコンパクトになるという文句を信じて購入しましたが個人的にはコンパクトになる(圧縮性)はあまり期待しない方がよいかと。それでも、Tシャツ、下着などを丸めて詰めればとてもコンパクトになり２気室あるので、使用前、使用済みなど使い分けができてとても便利です。自分は未使用の衣類はそのまま丸めて本品にいれて使用済みの衣類は圧縮袋かホテルにある洗濯袋にいれてから本品にパッキングしています。今は２～３泊の出張であれば本品と、同メーカの「トラベルポーチ パックイット フォルダー オーガナイザー 」を使って楽にパッキングしています。
Broke after only a few uses. For the price, I was expecting long-term use. Only put lightweight clothes in it. Not impressed. You can easily find more durable packing cubes at a more reasonable cost.
